  "id": "RAW_18bd0659",
  "title": "Gemini 3.1 Flash Live：让音频 AI 更自然、更可靠",
  "url": "https://deepmind.google/blog/gemini-3-1-flash-live-making-audio-ai-more-natural-and-reliable/",
  "date": "2026-03-26 15:23:20",
  "author": "Valeria Wu",
  "siteName": "Google DeepMind Blog",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div class=\"audio-player-tts\" data-component=\"uni-audio-player-tts\" uni-l10n=\"{\n       &quot;stop&quot;: &quot;Pause article audio description&quot;,\n       &quot;play&quot;: &quot;Play article audio description&quot;,\n       &quot;progress&quot;: &quot;Current audio progress minutes with seconds: [[progress]]&quot;,\n       &quot;duration&quot;: &quot;Duration of the audio minutes with seconds: [[duration]]&quot;,\n       &quot;settings&quot;: &quot;Click for settings&quot;,\n       &quot;timeText&quot;: &quot;[[duration]] minutes&quot;\n     }\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n      &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Audio TTS&quot;,\n      &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini 3.1 Flash Live: Making audio AI more natural and reliable&quot;\n     }\" data-tts-audios=\"[\n      \n        {&quot;voice_name&quot;: &quot;Umbriel&quot;,\n        &quot;voice_source&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/media/tts_audio_83935_umbriel_2026_03_26_15_29_05.wav&quot;,\n        &quot;mimetype&quot;: &quot;audio/x-wav&quot;},\n      \n        {&quot;voice_name&quot;: &quot;Gacrux&quot;,\n        &quot;voice_source&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/media/tts_audio_83935_gacrux_2026_03_26_15_25_52.wav&quot;,\n        &quot;mimetype&quot;: &quot;audio/x-wav&quot;}\n      ]\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n   <audio class=\"audio-player-tts__player\" title=\"Gemini 3.1 Flash Live: Making audio AI more natural and reliable\">\n    <source src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/media/tts_audio_83935_umbriel_2026_03_26_15_29_05.wav\" type=\"audio/x-wav\">\n    <p>Your browser does not support the audio element.</p>\n   </audio>\n   <div class=\"audio-player-tts__container\" aria-label=\"\">\n    <div class=\"audio-player-tts__content\">\n     <button class=\"audio-player-tts__preview-play\" aria-label=\"Play article audio description\">\n      <svg class=\"icon audio-player-tts__play-icon\">\n       <use xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" href=\"/static/blogv2/images/icons.svg?version=pr20260319-1641#ttf-play-spark\"></use>\n      </svg>\n     </button>\n     <div class=\"audio-player-tts__text-content\">\n      <span style=\"font-size:1rem;\">Today, we’re advancing Gemini’s real-time dialogue capabilities with Gemini 3.1 Flash Live, our highest-quality audio and voice model yet. It delivers the speed and natural rhythm needed for the next generation of voice-first AI, offering a more intuitive experience for developers, enterprises and everyday users.</span>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini 3.1 Flash Live: Making audio AI more natural and reliable&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"edks7\">3.1 Flash Live is available across Google products:</p>\n     <ul>\n      <li data-block-key=\"4llmk\">For developers in preview via the <a href=\"https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/live\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Gemini Live API</a> in <a href=\"http://ai.studio/live\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Google AI Studio</a></li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"d5qg7\">For enterprises in <a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/products/gemini-enterprise-for-customer-experience?e=48754805\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Gemini Enterprise for Customer Experience</a></li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"1cpod\">For everyone via <a href=\"https://blog.google/products-and-platforms/products/search/search-live-global-expansion\">Search Live</a> and <a href=\"https://gemini.google/overview/gemini-live/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Gemini Live</a></li>\n     </ul>\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"b0mkr\">For developers: Robust reasoning and task execution</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"9kef0\">We’ve improved 3.1 Flash Live’s overall quality, making it more reliable for developers and enterprises to build voice-first agents that can complete complex tasks at scale. On <a href=\"https://github.com/zai-org/ComplexFuncBench?tab=readme-ov-file\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">ComplexFuncBench Audio</a>, a benchmark that captures multi-step function calling with various constraints, it leads with a score of 90.8% compared to our previous model.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-full-width alignment=\"full\" alt-text=\"ComplexFuncBench audio bar graph\" external-image=\"\" or-mp4-video-title=\"\" or-mp4-video-url=\"\" section-header=\"Gemini 3.1 Flash Live: Making audio AI more natural and reliable\" external-link=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_images/gemini_flash_live__complexfuncbench__eval__light_Web.gif\" custom-class=\"image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" autoplay=\"true\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width--full image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Inline Images&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Gemini 3.1 Flash Live: Making audio AI more natural and reliable&quot;}\">\n    <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n    <a class=\" image-full-width__link \" href=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260327063155_gemini_flash_live__complexfuncbench__eval__light_Web.gif\" alt=\"ComplexFuncBench audio bar graph\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><!--?lit$93794141769$--> \n     <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset \">\n      <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n      <div slot=\"image-slot\" style=\"display: block;\">\n       <img alt=\"ComplexFuncBench audio bar graph\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260327063155_gemini_flash_live__complexfuncbench__eval__light_Web.gif\">\n      </div>\n      <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n      <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n      <!--?-->\n      <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n      <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n      <!--?-->\n      <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n      <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n      <!--?-->\n     </div></a> <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n    <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n    <!--?-->\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-full-width>\n  <uni-image-full-width alignment=\"full\" alt-text=\"BigBenchAudio bar graph\" external-image=\"\" or-mp4-video-title=\"\" or-mp4-video-url=\"\" section-header=\"Gemini 3.1 Flash Live: Making audio AI more natural and reliable\" external-link=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_images/gemini_flash_live__bigbenchaudio__eval__light_Web.gif\" custom-class=\"image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" autoplay=\"true\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width--full image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Inline Images&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Gemini 3.1 Flash Live: Making audio AI more natural and reliable&quot;}\">\n    <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n    <a class=\" image-full-width__link \" href=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260327063155_gemini_flash_live__bigbenchaudio__eval__light_Web.gif\" alt=\"BigBenchAudio bar graph\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><!--?lit$93794141769$--> \n     <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset \">\n      <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n      <div slot=\"image-slot\" style=\"display: block;\">\n       <img alt=\"BigBenchAudio bar graph\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260327063155_gemini_flash_live__bigbenchaudio__eval__light_Web.gif\">\n      </div>\n      <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n      <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n      <!--?-->\n      <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n      <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n      <!--?-->\n      <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n      <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n      <!--?-->\n     </div></a> <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n    <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n    <!--?-->\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-full-width>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini 3.1 Flash Live: Making audio AI more natural and reliable&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"30z86\">On Scale AI’s <a href=\"https://labs.scale.com/leaderboard/audiomc\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Audio MultiChallenge</a>, Gemini 3.1 Flash Live leads with a score of 36.1% with “thinking” on. The benchmark specifically tests complex instruction following and long-horizon reasoning amidst the interruptions and hesitations typical of real-world audio.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-full-width alignment=\"full\" alt-text=\"AudioMultiChallenge bar graph\" external-image=\"\" or-mp4-video-title=\"\" or-mp4-video-url=\"\" section-header=\"Gemini 3.1 Flash Live: Making audio AI more natural and reliable\" external-link=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_images/gemini_flash_live__audiomultichallenge__eval__light_Web.gif\" custom-class=\"image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" autoplay=\"true\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width--full image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Inline Images&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Gemini 3.1 Flash Live: Making audio AI more natural and reliable&quot;}\">\n    <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n    <a class=\" image-full-width__link \" href=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260327063155_gemini_flash_live__audiomultichallenge__eval__light_Web.gif\" alt=\"AudioMultiChallenge bar graph\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><!--?lit$93794141769$--> \n     <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset \">\n      <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n      <div slot=\"image-slot\" style=\"display: block;\">\n       <img alt=\"AudioMultiChallenge bar graph\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260327063155_gemini_flash_live__audiomultichallenge__eval__light_Web.gif\">\n      </div>\n      <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n      <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n      <!--?-->\n      <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n      <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n      <!--?-->\n      <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n      <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n      <!--?-->\n     </div></a> <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n    <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n    <!--?-->\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-full-width>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini 3.1 Flash Live: Making audio AI more natural and reliable&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"c5i4b\">3.1 Flash Live also has improved tonal understanding to deliver more natural dialogue. In <a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/products/gemini-enterprise-for-customer-experience?e=48754805\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Gemini Enterprise for Customer Experience</a>, it’s even more effective at recognizing acoustic nuances like pitch and pace than 2.5 Flash Native Audio. It’s also better at dynamically adjusting its response to users' expressions of frustration or confusion.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <section class=\"uni-component-spacing\">\n   <ui-carousel gap=\"24px\" analytics-module-name=\"Media Carousel\" analytics-section-header=\"Gemini 3.1 Flash Live: Making audio AI more natural and reliable\" loop=\"\" active-index=\"0\">\n    <!---->\n    <div class=\"ui-carousel\" role=\"region\" aria-roledescription=\"carousel\" aria-label=\"carousel\" style=\"--slides-per-view: 1; --slide-gap: 24px; --arrow-top-position: 272.5px;\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Media Carousel&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Gemini 3.1 Flash Live: Making audio AI more natural and reliable&quot;}\">\n     <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n     <button class=\"ui-carousel__arrow ui-carousel__arrow--previous\" aria-label=\"Previous item\" aria-controls=\"ui-carousel-10005758\"><uni-icon-component icon-id=\"carousel-arrow\" remove-viewbox=\"true\"><!----></uni-icon-component></button>\n     <button class=\"ui-carousel__arrow ui-carousel__arrow--next\" aria-label=\"Next item\" aria-controls=\"ui-carousel-10005758\"><uni-icon-component icon-id=\"carousel-arrow\" remove-viewbox=\"true\"><!----></uni-icon-component></button>\n     <div class=\"ui-carousel__slider\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-atomic=\"false\" id=\"ui-carousel-10005758\">\n      <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n      <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n      <!---->\n      <div class=\"ui-carousel__slide\" role=\"tabpanel\" id=\"ui-carousel-10005758-0\" data-index=\"0\">\n       <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n       <ui-carousel-slide analytics-module-name=\"Media Carousel Slide\" analytics-section-header=\"Gemini 3.1 Flash Live: Making audio AI more natural and reliable\" aspect-ratio=\"horizontal\" text-alignment=\"center\" headline=\"\" read-more=\"\">\n        <!---->\n        <div class=\" ui-carousel-slide \">\n         <div class=\"ui-carousel-slide__component-background\">\n          <div class=\" ui-carousel-slide__component \">\n           <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n           <div slot=\"content-block\" style=\"display: block;\">\n            <uni-image-full-width alignment=\"\" alt-text=\"Breakdown live demo video\" external-image=\"\" or-mp4-video-title=\"breakdown demo final\" or-mp4-video-url=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Breakdown_Live_demo_v5_w_disclaimer_small.mp4\" section-header=\"Gemini 3.1 Flash Live: Making audio AI more natural and reliable\" custom-class=\"image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\">\n             <!---->\n             <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width-- image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Inline Images&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Gemini 3.1 Flash Live: Making audio AI more natural and reliable&quot;}\">\n              <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n              <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n              <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset image-full-width__media-asset--mp4 \">\n               <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n               <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n               <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n               <uni-video-player muted playsinline=\"\" controls=\"\" type=\"video/mp4\" alt-text=\"Breakdown live demo video\" video-url=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Breakdown_Live_demo_v5_w_disclaimer_small.mp4\" tts-json=\"\" audio-descripted-video=\"\" section-header=\"Gemini 3.1 Flash Live: Making audio AI more natural and reliable\" video-title=\"breakdown demo final\">\n                <!---->\n                <div class=\"uni-video-player\">\n                 <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n                 <video crossorigin=\"anonymous\" preload=\"metadata\" muted playsinline=\"\" type=\"video/mp4\" aria-label=\"Breakdown live demo video\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Breakdown_Live_demo_v5_w_disclaimer_small.mp4#t=0.001\" class=\" uni-video-player__video reduce-motion-disabled \" title=\"breakdown demo final\" style=\"min-height:0px;\" poster=\"\">\n                  Sorry, your browser doesn't support embedded videos, but don't worry, you can <a download=\"\" href=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Breakdown_Live_demo_v5_w_disclaimer_small.mp4\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">download it</a> and watch it with your favorite video player!\n                 </video>\n                 <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n                 <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n                 <div class=\"uni-video-player__controls\">\n                  <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n                  <button class=\" uni-video-player__button uni-video-player__button--main uni-video-player__button--main--active \" aria-label=\"Play video\"><uni-icon-component icon-id=\"play-arrow\"><!----></uni-icon-component></button>\n                 </div>\n                 <!--?-->\n                </div>\n               </uni-video-player>\n               <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n               <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n               <!--?-->\n               <!--?-->\n               <!--?-->\n               <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n               <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n               <!--?-->\n               <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n               <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n               <!--?-->\n              </div>\n              <!--?-->\n              <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n              <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n              <!--?-->\n             </div>\n            </uni-image-full-width>\n           </div>\n           <slot></slot>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n         <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n         <div class=\"ui-carousel-slide__body\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Media Carousel Slide&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Gemini 3.1 Flash Live: Making audio AI more natural and reliable&quot;}\">\n          <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n          <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n          <div class=\" ui-carousel-slide__description \">\n           <div data-description-slot=\"\">\n            <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n            <div slot=\"description\" style=\"display: block;\"></div>\n           </div>\n           <div class=\"ui-carousel-slide__read-more-wrapper\">\n            <button class=\"ui-carousel-slide__read-more\"><!--?lit$93794141769$-->Read more</button>\n           </div>\n           <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n           <div class=\"ui-carousel-slide__paragraphs\">\n            <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n            <!---->\n            <p data-block-key=\"twove\">3.1 Flash Live lets you build voice-ready agents that handle complex tasks in noisy environments.</p>\n            <!---->\n           </div>\n          </div>\n          <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n          <div class=\"ui-carousel-slide__disclaimer\">\n           <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n           <div slot=\"disclaimer\" style=\"display: block;\">\n            <div class=\"rich-text\">\n             <p data-block-key=\"snbwd\">Illustrative demonstration built with Gemini 3.1 Pro, powered by Gemini 3.1 Flash Live.</p>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </ui-carousel-slide>\n      </div>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <!--?-->\n     </div>\n     <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n     <div class=\"ui-carousel__navigation\" role=\"tablist\">\n      <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n      <!---->\n      <button type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" class=\" ui-carousel__navigation-button ui-carousel__navigation-button--active \" aria-selected=\"true\" aria-controls=\"ui-carousel-10005758-0\" tabindex=\"0\"><!--?lit$93794141769$-->Jump to position 1</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" class=\" ui-carousel__navigation-button \" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"ui-carousel-10005758-1\" tabindex=\"-1\"><!--?lit$93794141769$-->Jump to position 2</button>\n      <!---->\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </ui-carousel>\n  </section>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini 3.1 Flash Live: Making audio AI more natural and reliable&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"hwo0j\">Companies like Verizon, LiveKit and The Home Depot have given positive feedback on 3.1 Flash Live in their workflows, highlighting its improved, natural conversation.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <section class=\"uni-component-spacing\">\n   <ui-carousel gap=\"24px\" analytics-module-name=\"Media Carousel\" analytics-section-header=\"Gemini 3.1 Flash Live: Making audio AI more natural and reliable\" loop=\"\" active-index=\"0\">\n    <!---->\n    <div class=\"ui-carousel\" role=\"region\" aria-roledescription=\"carousel\" aria-label=\"carousel\" style=\"--slides-per-view: 1; --slide-gap: 24px; --arrow-top-position: 272.5px;\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Media Carousel&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Gemini 3.1 Flash Live: Making audio AI more natural and reliable&quot;}\">\n     <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n     <button class=\"ui-carousel__arrow ui-carousel__arrow--previous\" aria-label=\"Previous item\" aria-controls=\"ui-carousel-16602042\"><uni-icon-component icon-id=\"carousel-arrow\" remove-viewbox=\"true\"><!----></uni-icon-component></button>\n     <button class=\"ui-carousel__arrow ui-carousel__arrow--next\" aria-label=\"Next item\" aria-controls=\"ui-carousel-16602042\"><uni-icon-component icon-id=\"carousel-arrow\" remove-viewbox=\"true\"><!----></uni-icon-component></button>\n     <div class=\"ui-carousel__slider\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-atomic=\"false\" id=\"ui-carousel-16602042\">\n      <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n      <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n      <!---->\n      <div class=\"ui-carousel__slide\" role=\"tabpanel\" id=\"ui-carousel-16602042-0\" data-index=\"0\">\n       <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n       <ui-carousel-slide analytics-module-name=\"Media Carousel Slide\" analytics-section-header=\"Gemini 3.1 Flash Live: Making audio AI more natural and reliable\" aspect-ratio=\"horizontal\" text-alignment=\"center\" headline=\"\" read-more=\"\">\n        <!---->\n        <div class=\" ui-carousel-slide \">\n         <div class=\"ui-carousel-slide__component-background\">\n          <div class=\" ui-carousel-slide__component \">\n           <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n           <div slot=\"content-block\" style=\"display: block;\">\n            <uni-image-full-width alignment=\"\" alt-text=\"Quote from The Home Depot\" external-image=\"\" or-mp4-video-title=\"\" or-mp4-video-url=\"\" section-header=\"Gemini 3.1 Flash Live: Making audio AI more natural and reliable\" custom-class=\"image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" autoplay=\"true\">\n             <!---->\n             <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width-- image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Inline Images&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Gemini 3.1 Flash Live: Making audio AI more natural and reliable&quot;}\">\n              <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n              <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n              <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset \">\n               <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n               <div slot=\"image-slot\" style=\"display: block;\">\n                <img alt=\"Quote from The Home Depot\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260327063155_gemini-3.1-flash_live_Enterprises.width-100.format-webp.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" data-loading=\"{\n            &quot;mobile&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/gemini-3.1-flash_live_Enterprises.width-500.format-webp.webp&quot;,\n            &quot;desktop&quot;: &quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/gemini-3.1-flash_live_Enterprise.width-1000.format-webp