s/Gemini_Live_3.1_Sizzle_Shortened_ALT_16x9_GC.mp4\" section-header=\"Gemini 3.1 Flash Live: Making audio AI more natural and reliable\" external-link=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8k8gzfaLDg4&amp;feature=youtu.be\" custom-class=\"image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width--full image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Inline Images&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Gemini 3.1 Flash Live: Making audio AI more natural and reliable&quot;}\">\n    <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n    <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n    <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset image-full-width__media-asset--mp4 \">\n     <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n     <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n     <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n     <uni-video-player muted playsinline=\"\" controls=\"\" type=\"video/mp4\" alt-text=\"Gemini 3.1, the biggest upgrade yet\" video-url=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Gemini_Live_3.1_Sizzle_Shortened_ALT_16x9_GC.mp4\" tts-json=\"\" audio-descripted-video=\"\" section-header=\"Gemini 3.1 Flash Live: Making audio AI more natural and reliable\" video-title=\"Gemini Live\">\n      <!---->\n      <div class=\"uni-video-player\">\n       <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n       <video crossorigin=\"anonymous\" preload=\"metadata\" muted playsinline=\"\" type=\"video/mp4\" aria-label=\"Gemini 3.1, the biggest upgrade yet\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Gemini_Live_3.1_Sizzle_Shortened_ALT_16x9_GC.mp4#t=0.001\" class=\" uni-video-player__video reduce-motion-disabled \" title=\"Gemini Live\" style=\"min-height:0px;\" poster=\"\">\n        Sorry, your browser doesn't support embedded videos, but don't worry, you can <a download=\"\" href=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/Gemini_Live_3.1_Sizzle_Shortened_ALT_16x9_GC.mp4\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">download it</a> and watch it with your favorite video player!\n       </video>\n       <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n       <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n       <div class=\"uni-video-player__controls\">\n        <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n        <button class=\" uni-video-player__button uni-video-player__button--main uni-video-player__button--main--active \" aria-label=\"Play video\"><uni-icon-component icon-id=\"play-arrow\"><!----></uni-icon-component></button>\n       </div>\n       <!--?-->\n      </div>\n     </uni-video-player>\n     <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n     <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n     <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n     <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n     <!--?-->\n    </div>\n    <!--?-->\n    <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n    <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n    <figcaption class=\"image-full-width__caption\">\n     <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n     <div slot=\"caption-slot\" style=\"display: block;\">\n      <div class=\"rich-text\">\n       <p data-block-key=\"j6gqb\">3.1 Flash Live makes Gemini Live faster and more helpful</p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n    </figcaption>\n    <!--?-->\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-full-width>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini 3.1 Flash Live: Making audio AI more natural and reliable&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"gtgm6\">3.1 Flash Live is also inherently multilingual, which enables this week’s <a href=\"https://blog.google/products-and-platforms/products/search/search-live-global-expansion\">global expansion of Search Live</a>. With this launch, people in more than 200 countries and territories can now have real-time, multimodal conversations with Search in their preferred language.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-full-width alignment=\"full\" alt-text=\"A video showing real-time troubleshooting help using 3.1 Flash Live\" external-image=\"\" or-mp4-video-title=\"AIM Search Live Shelf\" or-mp4-video-url=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/AIM_Search-Live_Shelf_1920x1080_NoDisclaimer.mp4\" section-header=\"Gemini 3.1 Flash Live: Making audio AI more natural and reliable\" custom-class=\"image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\">\n   <!---->\n   <div class=\"image-full-width image-full-width--full image-full-width--constrained-width uni-component-spacing\" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Inline Images&quot;,&quot;section_header&quot;:&quot;Gemini 3.1 Flash Live: Making audio AI more natural and reliable&quot;}\">\n    <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n    <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n    <div class=\" image-full-width__media-asset image-full-width__media-asset--mp4 \">\n     <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n     <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n     <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n     <uni-video-player muted playsinline=\"\" controls=\"\" type=\"video/mp4\" alt-text=\"A video showing real-time troubleshooting help using 3.1 Flash Live\" video-url=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/AIM_Search-Live_Shelf_1920x1080_NoDisclaimer.mp4\" tts-json=\"\" audio-descripted-video=\"\" section-header=\"Gemini 3.1 Flash Live: Making audio AI more natural and reliable\" video-title=\"AIM Search Live Shelf\">\n      <!---->\n      <div class=\"uni-video-player\">\n       <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n       <video crossorigin=\"anonymous\" preload=\"metadata\" muted playsinline=\"\" type=\"video/mp4\" aria-label=\"A video showing real-time troubleshooting help using 3.1 Flash Live\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/AIM_Search-Live_Shelf_1920x1080_NoDisclaimer.mp4#t=0.001\" class=\" uni-video-player__video reduce-motion-disabled \" title=\"AIM Search Live Shelf\" style=\"min-height:0px;\" poster=\"\">\n        Sorry, your browser doesn't support embedded videos, but don't worry, you can <a download=\"\" href=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/original_videos/AIM_Search-Live_Shelf_1920x1080_NoDisclaimer.mp4\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">download it</a> and watch it with your favorite video player!\n       </video>\n       <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n       <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n       <div class=\"uni-video-player__controls\">\n        <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n        <button class=\" uni-video-player__button uni-video-player__button--main uni-video-player__button--main--active \" aria-label=\"Play video\"><uni-icon-component icon-id=\"play-arrow\"><!----></uni-icon-component></button>\n       </div>\n       <!--?-->\n      </div>\n     </uni-video-player>\n     <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n     <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n     <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n     <!--?-->\n     <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n     <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n     <!--?-->\n    </div>\n    <!--?-->\n    <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n    <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n    <figcaption class=\"image-full-width__caption\">\n     <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n     <div slot=\"caption-slot\" style=\"display: block;\">\n      <div class=\"rich-text\">\n       <p data-block-key=\"wiveu\">Get real-time troubleshooting help using 3.1 Flash Live in Search Live</p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n    </figcaption>\n    <!--?-->\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-full-width>\n  <uni-youtube-player-article index=\"14\" thumbnail-alt=\"Search Live YouTube video\" subtitle=\"Search Live is enabling real-time multimodal conversations in more languages\" video-id=\"WQobm4_ixEU\" video-type=\"video\">\n   <!---->\n   <div data-yt-video=\"module\" class=\"article-video-special h-c-page--mobile-full-bleed \" data-analytics-module=\"{&quot;module_name&quot;:&quot;Youtube Video&quot;}\">\n    <div class=\"article-video-special__container\">\n     <div class=\"article-module uni-article-video uni-article-video--body\" data-component=\"uni-article-yt-player\" data-page-title=\"\" data-video-id=\"WQobm4_ixEU\" data-index-id=\"14\" data-type=\"video\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n      <button class=\"h-c-video h-c-video--marquee uni-article-video__custom-wrapper\" tabindex=\"0\">\n       <div class=\"uni-article-video__aspect-image\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260327063155_default.webp\" alt=\"Search Live YouTube video\" data-loading=\"{\n                    &quot;desktop&quot;: &quot;https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/WQobm4_ixEU/sddefault.webp&quot;,\n                    &quot;mobile&quot;: &quot;https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/WQobm4_ixEU/mqdefault.webp&quot;\n                  }\"><uni-icon-component class=\"uni-article-video__icon-wrapper\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__play-button--active\" remove-viewbox=\"true\" icon-id=\"yt_video_play_button_no_hole\"><!----></uni-icon-component><uni-icon-component class=\"uni-article-video__icon-wrapper\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__play-button\" custom-role=\"img\" remove-viewbox=\"true\" icon-id=\"yt_video_play_button\" custom-label=\"Video Title \"><!----></uni-icon-component><!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n        <div class=\"uni-article-video__duration loading\">\n         <uni-icon-component icon-id=\"yt_video_duration\" custom-class=\"uni-article-video__duration-icon\" remove-viewbox=\"true\"><!----></uni-icon-component><span class=\"uni-article-video__duration-time\">00:00</span>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </button>\n      <div class=\" uni-article-video__caption kw-speakable-hidden \">\n       <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n       <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n       <p class=\"uni-article-video__caption--subtitle\"><!--?lit$93794141769$-->Search Live is enabling real-time multimodal conversations in more languages</p>\n       <!--?lit$93794141769$-->\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </uni-youtube-player-article>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Gemini 3.1 Flash Live: Making audio AI more natural and reliable&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"2ug1k\">All audio generated by 3.1 Flash Live is watermarked with SynthID. This imperceptible watermark is interwoven directly into the audio output, allowing the reliable detection of AI-generated content to help prevent misinformation. For more information on our approach to safety and responsibility, see the <a href=\"https://deepmind.google/models/model-cards/gemini-3-1-flash-live\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">model card</a>.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"92o46\">Experience the naturalness and reliability of 3.1 Flash Live, starting today. We look forward to seeing how you interact and build with it.<span class=\"tombstone\"></span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Google DeepMind 发布了 Gemini 3.1 Flash Live，这是一款针对实时、自然语音交互进行优化的高质量音频模型，具备增强的推理能力和多步函数调用功能。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Google DeepMind 发布了 Gemini 3.1 Flash Live，这是一款针对实时、自然语音交互进行优化的高质量音频模型，具备增强的推理能力和多步函数调用功能。",
  "summary": "Gemini 3.1 Flash Live 代表了实时对话 AI 的重大进步，专注于速度、自然节奏和可靠性。该模型在复杂推理方面表现出色，以 90.8% 的得分在 ComplexFuncBench Audio 基准测试中处于领先地位。它引入了改进的语调理解能力，能够识别音高和语速，从而对用户的挫败感做出更具同理心的回应。对于开发者而言，它可通过 Gemini Live API 使用，支持稳健的任务执行，且对话线程长度是之前版本的两倍。安全性方面，所有生成的音频都集成了 SynthID 水印。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "音频任务中的顶尖推理能力。",
      "explanation": "该模型在 ComplexFuncBench Audio 上取得了 90.8% 的得分，展示了其在多步函数调用和复杂指令遵循方面的卓越能力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "增强的情感和语调智能。",
      "explanation": "通过识别音高和语速等声学细微差别，模型可以根据用户表达的挫败感或困惑调整其回应，使交互更加自然。"
    },
    {
      "point": "显著的性能和上下文改进。",
      "explanation": "Gemini 3.1 Flash Live 提供了更快的响应时间，并且能够保持对话线程的时间是其前身的两倍。"
    },
    {
      "point": "集成的安全性和全球可访问性。",
      "explanation": "该模型包含用于内容溯源的 SynthID 水印，并通过 Search Live 支持 200 多个国家的多种语言交互。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "它提供了下一代语音优先 AI 所需的速度和自然节奏。",
    "在 ComplexFuncBench Audio 上……它以 90.8% 的得分领先于我们之前的模型。",
    "与之前的模型相比，Gemini Live 提供了更快的响应，并且能够跟踪您的对话线程的时间是其两倍。",
    "所有由 3.1 Flash Live 生成的音频都带有 SynthID 水印……从而可以可靠地检测 AI 生成的内容。"
  ],
